item.title: CVE-2023-0539|2023-02-27T15:24:35.760Z -- unknown -- gs%20insever%20portfolio
item.description: The GS Insever Portfolio WordPress plugin before 1.4.5 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
